headline: Assessing PLDT (PSE:TEL) Valuation After Recent Downtrend and Fading Shareholder Returns
summary: PLDT (PSE:TEL) shares have been steadily watched by investors, especially as the company posts modest revenue and net income growth this year. Its stock performance offers some interesting trends for those tracking long-term value in the sector. See our latest analysis for PLDT. PLDT’s share price has slipped nearly 15% over the past three months, and year-to-date price returns remain in the red. Despite a five-year total shareholder return of almost 19%, the recent momentum has been fading...
